WEBVTT

00:01.373 --> 00:02.322
There are two kinds of folks

00:02.379 --> 00:03.979
who sit around thinking
about how to kill people:

00:04.313 --> 00:06.039
Psychopaths
and mystery writers.

00:06.277 --> 00:07.299
I'm the kind that pays better.

00:07.700 --> 00:08.300
Who am I?

00:08.389 --> 00:09.528
I'm Rick Castle.

00:09.529 --> 00:09.929
Castle.

00:09.963 --> 00:10.623
Castle.

00:10.624 --> 00:12.324
I really am ruggedly handsome,
aren't I?

00:12.378 --> 00:14.568
Every writer needs inspiration.
And I found mine.

00:14.778 --> 00:15.597
Detective Kate Beckett.

00:15.844 --> 00:17.111
Beckett.
Aah!

00:17.384 --> 00:19.469
Beckett?
Could you get some backup, please?

00:19.820 --> 00:21.704
<i>And thanks to my friendship</i>
<i>with the Mayor,</i>

00:21.755 --> 00:23.389
<i>I get to be on her case.</i>
Oh!

00:23.423 --> 00:25.992
Do I look like a killer to you?
Yes, you kill my patience.

00:26.026 --> 00:27.660
<i>And together,</i>
<i>we catch killers.</i>

00:28.208 --> 00:31.410
I hate this case.
I know. Isn't it great?

00:38.383 --> 00:39.084
Where'd he go?!

00:39.183 --> 00:41.918
I lost him.

00:41.952 --> 00:44.137
I think he went through here!

